=item LPAD(S,N,C)
String:
Takes the first argument (subject) string, and left pads it out to the
length specified in the second argument, using the first character of
the optional third argument.  If the third argument is missing, or is
the null string, spaces will be used for padding.  The subject will be
returned unmodified if already long enough.
I<SPITBOL? Extension, added in CSNOBOL4 version ?.?>.

