I<Extension from SPITBOL, added in CSNOBOL4 version 0.98.4>.

=item THAW(TABLE)
Data: restores normal entry creation behavior after B<FREEZE()>.
I<Extension from SNOBOL4+, added in CSNOBOL4 version 0.98.2>.

